      • org.eclipse.scada.vi.model.impl.SymbolImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Symbol

    public class SymbolImpl
extends EObjectImpl
implements Symbol
    An implementation of the model object 'Symbol'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Root
    • Properties
    • On Init
    • On Dispose
    • On Update
    • Script Modules
    • Cursors
    • Background Color
    • Design Size
    • Connections
